<p class="is-size-3 mb-1">About Experse</p>

<p>Experse is a decentralized discussion board and content aggregator. Users are able to create universes, which are dedicated to a certain topic or interest. Users can then post to universes, optionally entering a hyperlink to the content to discuss. Other users can then comment on theses posts, and helpful/interesting posts can be upvoted, whilst unhelpful/spammy posts can be downvoted. Users can also edit posts, and view edit history.</p>
